  "summary": "Mattermost doesn't validate CSRF tokens on an authentication endpoint",
  "details": "Mattermost versions 10.11.x \u003c= 10.11.12, 11.5.x \u003c= 11.5.0, 11.4.x \u003c= 11.4.2, 11.3.x \u003c= 11.3.2 fail to validate CSRF tokens on an authentication endpoint which allows an attacker to update a user's authentication method via a CSRF attack by tricking a user into visiting a malicious page. Mattermost Advisory ID: MMSA-2026-00625.",
